    "summary": "Redundant fallback in toolName resolution: when updTitle exists and updId exists, line 758 just wrote updTitle into _toolTitles, so `session._toolTitles?.get(updId)` already returns updTitle and the `?? updTitle` arm only matters when updId is undefined. Simpler and precedence-explicit: `updTitle ?? (updId ? session._toolTitles?.get(updId) : undefined) ?? \"tool\"` — one map lookup, no hidden write-then-read dependency.",
